<plot>A grandfather, a grandson, a very tender lesson in love. An urban coming of age movie set in the Brooklyn/Queens area with an Italian backdrop. From street punks and violence to an old mans fig tree in his backyard, this film can promise an emotional experience that will warm hearts and instill fear while examining what can happen when the raw emotions of a human being loses control; even for only a fleeting moment in time.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?248605</url></doc>
